(42, 7, 50, 41, 5, 34, 34, 'thy faith hath saved thee', 'Connection of Faith and Healing', 'Both passages emphasize the role of faith in achieving peace and wholeness. The phrases ''thy faith hath saved thee'' and ''thy faith hath made thee whole'' highlight the transformative power of faith in both contexts.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 7, 50, 42, 8, 48, 48, 'go in peace', 'Connection of Faith and Peace', 'Both passages emphasize the role of faith in healing and salvation. They conclude with the phrase ''go in peace,'' highlighting a common theme of peace following faith.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 7, 50, 42, 18, 42, 42, 'thy faith hath saved thee', 'Connection of Faith and Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the role of faith in salvation. In each instance, Jesus declares that faith is the means by which individuals receive healing or salvation.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
