(42, 7, 50, 49, 2, 8, 10, 'Thy faith hath saved thee', 'Connection of Faith and Salvation', 'This connection highlights the theme of salvation through faith. Both passages emphasize that faith is essential for receiving God''s grace and being saved.', 'theme', 0.825, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
